@startuml uc-5_analyze_stats
!include ../../_theme.iuml

title UC-5 — Analyze stats

|Student|
start
:Select a species or instance;
|System|
if (Species?) then (yes)
    :Read base `StatBlock` via `species.base_stats`;
else (instance)
    :Call `PokemonInstance.effective_stats()`;
    :Apply `Nature.modifier_for(stat)` multipliers;
endif
:Populate the Stats tab (JSON payload);
|Student|
:Focus the Stats tab (`]` or click);
|System|
:Render HP / Attack / Defense / Sp.Atk / Sp.Def / Speed;
|Student|
if (Inspect stat classes?) then (yes)
    :Click `StatBlock`, `HPStat`, etc. in relationships;
    |System|
    :Focus UML on the clicked stat class;
endif
stop

@enduml
